GardenActivity:navHost(startDestination to HomeVpFragment)
-HomeVPFragment:ViewPager2(From adapter creates 2 fragments below)
--Tab1:GardenFragment(If list empty, there is a Add Plant button with onClick to PlantListFragment
                      Each item onCLick navigate into PlantDetailFragment)
--Tab2:PlantListFragment(right top icon is filter_zone, it will return filtered plants to the list)
---PlantDetailFragment(uses compose to setContent, calling PlantDetailsScreen/View
